---
title: Spanish Style Veggie Rice with Peppers, Mushrooms and Tomatoes
description: Requiring minimal effort, but resulting in maximum flavour, our veggie Spanish-style rice takes ‘one-pot wonders’ to new heights. Whilst ingredients like rosemary and turmeric wouldn’t normally be found in a traditional paella, we’ve given it a HelloFresh twist to create a recipe we know you’re going to love. Place this colourful dish in the middle of your table and enjoy in a traditional, communal style!
